'''King&#39;s Festival Calendar''' is an ancient Egyptian festival ==Overview== The {{ill|Ancient Egypt|de|Altes Ägypten|ja|Ancient Egypt|zh|Ancient Egypt|lt=Ancient Egyptian|lt_de=altägyptische|lt_ja=Ancient Egyptian|lt_zh=Ancient Egyptian|qq=draft}} '''King's Festival Calendar''' (also '''Royal Festivals, Renewal Festivals''') comprised only {{ill|Procession|de|Prozession|ja|Procession|zh|Procession|qq=draft}}s, which served to confirm and renew the reigning ruler.
