enewal and confirmation festival. |- | {{ill|Sokar Festival|de|Sokar-Fest|ja|Sokar Festival|zh|Sokar Festival|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sokar Festival|qq=}} | Royal renewal and confirmation festival. |- | {{ill|Nehebkau Festival|de|Neheb-kau-Fest|ja|Nehebkau Festival|zh|Nehebkau Festival|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nehebkau Festival|qq=}} | Royal renewal and confirmation festival with New Year characteristics. |- | [[:en:Beautiful Festival of the Valley|Valley Festival]] | [[:en:New Kingdom of Egypt|New Kingdom]]: royal renewal and confirmation festival. |- | {{ill|Amun-Re Festival|de|Amun-Re-Fest|ja|Amun-Re Festival|zh|Amun-Re Festival|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Amun-Re Festival|qq=}} | New Kingdom: royal renewal and confirmation festival. |- | [[:en:Opet Festival|Opet Festival]] | New Kingdom: royal renewal and confirmation festival. |- | [[:en:Sed festival|Sed Festival]] | Royal renewal and confirmation festival. |- | Death of the King | Burial by his designated successor and transition into the [[:en:Duat|Duat]] as ''son of [[:en:Osiris|Osiris]]''. |- |}
